```

---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£7Ô∏è‚É£ SECURITY & GOVERNANCE CONTROLS

* MFA for evaluators
* Session timeout
* Score submission deadline
* Role validation (Logic 2)
* Immutable logs
* Conflict-of-interest validation before scoring

---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£8Ô∏è‚É£ EDGE CASE HANDLING

* Evaluator fails to submit score
* Deadlocked scoring spread
* Tie scores
* Arithmetic anomalies
* Court-ordered re-evaluation
* Discovered compliance violation mid-evaluation

Tie-breaking rule must be predefined.

---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£9Ô∏è‚É£ KPI METRICS

* Evaluation duration
* Score variance rate
* Outlier frequency
* Re-evaluation frequency
* Post-award dispute rate
* Score override frequency
* Tie occurrence rate

---

# 2Ô∏è‚É£0Ô∏è‚É£ COMMON FAILURE POINTS (TO DESIGN AGAINST)

* Unstructured scoring
* Weight manipulation
* Manual ranking adjustment
* Hidden criteria
* No written justification
* Financial influence on technical review

System must technically prevent these weaknesses.

